729024f-a.title: Richmond: Innis Street - St. Joseph's Avenue
729024f-a.text:
Innis Street, at the N.W. corner of St. Joseph's Avenue, show-
ing the Port Richmond High School. The view is northeastward from
near John Street. The 2Y0 - story house is No. 79 Innis Street.
March 24, 1928
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
